and do proper work, can he?

178
00:12:27,079 --> 00:12:27,999
Right, boss.

179
00:12:34,170 --> 00:12:37,130
Look, here's what I want to say.

180
00:12:38,716 --> 00:12:41,466
I put you in charge, not Tanabe.

181
00:12:41,552 --> 00:12:43,852
Don't embarrass me.

182
00:12:43,929 --> 00:12:44,809
