218
00:15:23,255 --> 00:15:24,165
Yeah, water…

219
00:15:24,256 --> 00:15:26,546
Water. Don't you want it hot?

220
00:15:26,634 --> 00:15:28,224
-Hot.
-Hot water, right.

221
00:15:39,605 --> 00:15:40,895
-Any more?
-Uh…

222
00:15:40,981 --> 00:15:42,821
-Isn't that crazy?
-Shh!

223
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,820
-Quiet!
-See you.

224
00:15:46,111 --> 00:15:47,571
-Come here.
-Oh!

225
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,740
Don't tell anyone!

226
00:15:49,823 --> 00:15:51,953
So some men really can get pregnant!

227
00:15:52,034 --> 00:15:53,044
Keep it down.

228
00:15:53,535 --> 00:15:55,075
Please, you can't tell anyone.

229
00:15:56,664 --> 00:15:58,964
