238
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,360
But you know,

239
00:16:25,275 --> 00:16:27,065
it's a pretty great time to be alive

240
00:16:27,152 --> 00:16:29,112
where cisgender men can give birth.

241
00:16:29,196 --> 00:16:30,316
-What?
-No?

242
00:16:31,031 --> 00:16:34,831
