243
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:38,500
Nausea and headaches for months.

244
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:41,540
People nagging you constantly
until it's born,

245
00:16:41,625 --> 00:16:44,125
like, "Don't eat this,
move that, go for a walk."

246
00:16:44,211 --> 00:16:46,761
You can't drink or eat raw stuff.

247
00:16:46,839 --> 00:16:48,379
