251
00:17:01,437 --> 00:17:02,267
Hey.

252
00:17:03,188 --> 00:17:06,938
I know you're not interested in marriage.
But what about kids?

253
00:17:08,318 --> 00:17:10,198
Don't you want him to have the baby?

254
00:17:11,238 --> 00:17:14,408
What? I've never thought about it.

255
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:19,290
Okay, well.

256
00:17:20,164 --> 00:17:22,254
Maybe think about it before deciding.

257
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:27,755
Because no matter who gives birth,

258
00:17:28,422 --> 00:17:30,512
pregnancy is a freaking miracle.

259
00:18:03,791 --> 00:18:05,711
Sorry I'm late.

260
00:18:06,418 --> 00:18:10,258
No, I'm sorry about yesterday.
I was in such a state.

261
00:18:13,050 --> 00:18:16,140
It's not your fault. You're pregnant.

262
00:18:20,307 --> 00:18:22,427
Hello, here's some water.

263
00:18:22,518 --> 00:18:24,098
