-Thanks.

264
00:18:24,186 --> 00:18:25,146
I'll be right back.

265
00:18:32,861 --> 00:18:35,411
All I can eat right now is sweet stuff.

266
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:41,870
I've lost two kilos this week.

267
00:18:43,247 --> 00:18:44,077
Oh, yeah.

268
00:18:45,624 --> 00:18:46,794
I got a new copy.

269
00:18:50,295 --> 00:18:51,125
Go ahead.

270
00:18:51,213 --> 00:18:53,343
ABORTION CONSENT FORM

271
00:18:53,423 --> 00:18:54,263
Here.

272
00:19:05,561 --> 00:19:06,521
But, you know…

273
00:19:08,897 --> 00:19:12,607
think about this situation.

274
00:19:14,695 --> 00:19:16,695
It's really a blessing.

275
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:18,530
For people who want kids, sure.

276
00:19:18,615 --> 00:19:22,445
No, I mean for a man to get pregnant.

277
00:19:24,204 --> 00:19:27,674
If you were willing to give birth,

278
00:19:27,749 --> 00:19:30,999
I could have a kid
without having to give birth myself.

279
00:19:33,213 --> 00:19:37,683
Plus, you're an ad man.

280
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:41,350
Being a pregnant man
could work to your advantage

281
00:19:42,848 --> 00:19:44,808
and lead to new job opportunities.

282
00:19:46,894 --> 00:19:48,484
When I think of it like that,

283
00:19:49,396 --> 00:19:51,106
I start thinking that perhaps

284
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:54,820
this is actually a huge stroke of luck.

285
00:19:56,153 --> 00:19:56,993
Look, Aki.

286
00:19:58,614 --> 00:20:00,914
I'm actually pregnant.

287
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:03,790
-I get it.
-You don't.

288
00:20:03,869 --> 00:20:06,959
I feel queasy all day.
My boss is watching me.

289
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:10,209
It's already destroying my life.
Don't joke with me.

290
00:20:12,794 --> 00:20:13,844
Sorry.

291
00:20:15,923 --> 00:20:18,683
I agree that we won't have the baby.

292
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:20,639
It's not just about agreeing.

293
00:20:21,929 --> 00:20:24,009
Don't make it sound so easy.

294
00:20:25,224 --> 00:20:28,604
I have to harm my body for an abortion.

295
00:20:29,728 --> 00:20:31,058
Sure, but still.

296
00:20:35,234 --> 00:20:38,284
You sound just like one of those guys.

297
00:20:39,613 --> 00:20:42,243
Men who get girls pregnant
then say, "Oh, I understand,"

298
00:20:42,324 --> 00:20:44,834
and sign the form
like it's none of their business.

299
00:20:46,161 --> 00:20:50,921
But I'm the one who bears the risk
whether it's childbirth or an abortion.

300
00:20:52,668 --> 00:20:53,878
Hurry up and sign it.

301
00:20:59,091 --> 00:20:59,931
Yes.

302
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,360
Stamp it, too.

303
00:21:50,058 --> 00:21:51,768
-Hello there.
-Hey.

304
00:21:52,269 --> 00:21:54,479
We've got a UNIVE meeting at 3:00 p.m.

305
00:21:54,563 --> 00:21:55,653
Is room A3 free?

306
00:21:56,481 --> 00:21:58,901
The monitors are hard to see
in the usual room.

307
00:21:59,651 --> 00:22:01,151
The meeting's already started.

308
00:22:13,874 --> 00:22:16,214
-Thanks.
-Thank you.

309
00:22:16,293 --> 00:22:17,633
See you.

310
00:22:17,711 --> 00:22:20,921
Sorry, I forgot to check
for any schedule changes.

311
00:22:21,006 --> 00:22:23,676
It's fine. You're not feeling well.

312
00:22:24,301 --> 00:22:26,801
-It was short notice.
-I'm sorry.

313
00:22:27,637 --> 00:22:29,677
Given the circumstances,

314
00:22:29,765 --> 00:22:32,345
I'd like to hand this project over

315
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:34,234
to Tanabe to manage.

316
00:22:34,311 --> 00:22:38,151
What? But this plan was my idea.

317
00:22:38,231 --> 00:22:40,441
The plan is a team effort.

318
00:22:41,026 --> 00:22:44,906
You shouldn't have to
keep shouldering it all for the company.

319
00:22:44,988 --> 00:22:46,618
-No, but--
-Hiyama.

320
00:22:46,698 --> 00:22:48,698
Accept help when you're having trouble.

321
00:22:49,326 --> 00:22:51,196
I'll work to the best of my abilities.

322
00:22:51,286 --> 00:22:53,156
Wait, how do we tell the client?

323
00:22:53,246 --> 00:22:54,996
This is a joint decision.

324
00:22:56,291 --> 00:22:58,921
You turn up at the office poorly dressed.

325
00:22:59,002 --> 00:23:02,462
Your mind's elsewhere,
you can't communicate properly.

326
00:23:03,173 --> 00:23:06,763
I mean, where were you today?

327
00:23:06,843 --> 00:23:08,933
We couldn't get a hold of you.

328
00:23:09,846 --> 00:23:12,016
Seeing you like this lately,

329
00:23:12,099 --> 00:23:15,349
we decided it would be best for the team.

330
00:23:15,852 --> 00:23:17,312
Alright?

331
00:23:17,396 --> 00:23:19,266
-Take care of it, Tanabe.
-Yes.

332
00:23:20,107 --> 00:23:21,817
Right. Please tidy things up here.

333
00:23:22,609 --> 00:23:24,279
Then read the minutes

334
00:23:24,903 --> 00:23:27,573
and prepare the necessary materials
for next time.

335
00:23:31,076 --> 00:23:32,286
Koga, you can leave.

336
00:23:47,467 --> 00:23:52,347
KENTARO HIYAMA
DUE IN 206 DAYS

337
00:23:57,436 --> 00:23:58,766
<i>Dropped down the ranks, huh?</i>

338
00:23:58,854 --> 00:24:00,774
<i>I'd like to do the procedure ASAP.</i>

339
00:24:00,856 --> 00:24:01,726
Are you pregnant?

340
00:24:01,815 --> 00:24:03,105
-Boobs.
-I know!

341
00:24:03,191 --> 00:24:05,491
<i>It's not as easy as you think.</i>

342
00:24:05,569 --> 00:24:07,359
<i>What do you think, Mr. Hiyama?</i>

343
00:25:02,584 --> 00:25:06,424
